				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Raw Silk armor comes after Patchwork, which becomes trivial at 39					<BR>
Combine patterns with silk swatches (made from 2 &quot;spider&quot; silks) to make garments.  		<BR>
<BR>
Garment     Patterns    Swatches    AC<BR>
Cord        belt        1           2<BR>
Cloak       cloak       1           3<BR>
Collar      gorget      1           2<BR>
Gloves      glove       1           3<BR>
Headband                1           3<BR>
Mantle	    shoulderpad 1           2<BR>
Pants	    pants       2           4<BR>
Robe        tunic       2           6<BR>
Sandals     boot        1           3<BR>
Sleeves     sleeve      1           3<BR>
Veil        mask        1           2<BR>
Wristband   wristband   1           2
