also with heady kiola [made from brewers or 2 kiola saps, 1 water flask (not summoned or forged) and a bottle] and silk swatches (2 spider silks) you can make cured silk which is monk only, and from what i hear, pretty hard to make (not sure on skill level but i think its on par with mater). all below is cured silk armor. all of these require apporite pattern.<BR>
<BR>
Name          AC     Silk Swatches    Heady Kiola<BR>
Mask           2          1                1<BR>
Headband       ?          ?                ?<BR>
Collar         ?          1                2<BR>
